title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 752-1.2 - Physician's assistants and specialist's assistants
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 752-1.2 - Physician's assistants and specialist's assistants

State Regulations

The services of physician's assistants and specialist's
assistants shall be provided in compliance with the requirements of Parts 94
and 707 of this Title. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
752-1.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
